NOTICE

This package is a reimplementation of Moti (https://moti.fyi/),
originally authored by Fernando Rojo and released under the MIT License:

  Copyright (c) 2021 Fernando Rojo
  https://github.com/nandorojo/moti

The API design, animation model, and portions of the worklet logic are
derived from Moti. This reimplementation targets react-native-reanimated 4
and react-native 0.86+, which introduced breaking changes incompatible with
the upstream Moti package at the time of writing.
